      to its end customer are conditioned upon Supplier’s acceptance of Fictiv’s Vendor Terms and Conditions of Sale. Accordingly,
      Vendor acknowledges and agrees that Fictiv accepts Vendor’s offer to manufacture or provide services on the express
      condition that Fictiv’s Vendor Terms and Conditions of Sale apply to the transaction between Fictiv and Vendor, and any
      terms or conditions on Vendor's documentation, other than description of the Product or Service, and their quantity, price
      and delivery date, are deemed rejected and are to be ignored unless the identical terms describing the product, service or the
      performance related thereto appear on this Purchase Order.



      
    
  






